Nxt (CURRENCY:NXT) traded 7.1% lower against the US dollar during the 24-hour period ending at 14:00 PM E.T. on February 16th. Nxt has a total market cap of $246.66 million and $20.41 million worth of Nxt was traded on exchanges in the last day. During the last week, Nxt has traded 26% higher against the US dollar. One Nxt coin can now be bought for about $0.25 or 0.00002485 BTC on cryptocurrency exchanges including AEX, Livecoin, Nxt Asset Exchange and Poloniex..
