Buying and Selling Nxt.
`_____ `__ `______ 1___ 
Nxt can be traded on the following cryptocurrency exchanges: Livecoin, CoinEgg, Stocks.Exchange, C-CEX, Bitcoin Indonesia, Nxt Asset Exchange, HitBTC, Bittrex, AEX, Poloniex, SouthXchange and LiteBit.eu. It is not currently possible to purchase Nxt directly using U.S. dollars. Investors seeking to acquire Nxt must first purchase Ethereum or Bitcoin using an exchange that deals in U.S. dollars such as Changelly, GDAX or Gemini. Investors can then use their newly-acquired Ethereum or Bitcoin to purchase Nxt using one of the aforementioned exchanges..
